### Why this is the senior move:

It gives you:

* Centralized logic
* Safer data access
* Easier testing
* Reusable patterns
* Clean separation of concerns

And most importantly:

> It forces you to actually understand your system

---

# **If I Were Guiding You Next Week**

Focus ONLY on this:

