- After scrolling past 80px: navbar shrinks horizontally (add mx-4 md:mx-8), becomes floating (position stays fixed, add rounded-2xl), gains solid background color #1e3a5f, adds a subtle shadow (shadow-lg), and slightly reduces vertical padding
- Transition between states must be smooth — use Tailwind's `transition-all duration-300` classes
- Navbar must always be `fixed top-4 left-0 right-0 z-50` so it stays visible on scroll

