## **UX / Mobile (dnd-kit + TouchSensor)**

**Rating: B+ to A-**

This is one of your strongest areas.

Most devs ignore mobile edge cases completely.

If you actually tuned:

* activation constraints
* touch delays
* scroll conflicts

